to do stand up, right. He's

00:02:45.831 --> 00:02:48.267
like, "Gotta do your time, man.
It's the most important thing.

00:02:48.300 --> 00:02:51.237
That's the rules of the road,
you gotta do your time." And

00:02:51.270 --> 00:02:54.340
right before I was about to go
on stage, he recited some poem

00:02:54.373 --> 00:02:57.510
that he had written about the
road to me before I went on. I

00:02:57.543 --> 00:02:59.979
wish to hell I could remember
it, but it was sort of like a

00:03:00.012 --> 00:03:03.482
